Girl I know what it’s like to get knocked down time and time again 

Especially these last few years 

Do you feel me?! 🙋🏻‍♀️

I’ve had seasons of life where I’ve been making 6 figures, financially free, living all over the world 

I’ve also had seasons where I’ve lived with my family to save money and felt stuck, lost, and confused in my business (and life in general) 

Being an entrepreneur can be fucking hard 
Being a highly sensitive person can be fucking hard 
Being a woman can be fucking hard 

Being all 3 of the above, if you’re like me girl you feel me…that sometimes it being fucking hard is an understatement 😂

It doesn’t have to feel so hard though 

What’s helped me the most to dig myself out of these tough seasons of business (and life) is having the right SUPPORT 

We aren’t meant to do this alone 

My healer, my mentors, my yoga studio, and my sisters have been what’s helped me transform the hardest year of my life (2022) in to the best year of my life I’ve had in a decade 

They helped build me up when I lost my confidence and my way 

I’m so passionate about helping support women for this same reason 

I want to help you feel like a badass bitch 

To not feel lost 

To not feel alone 

I’ll always share what I’m going through on here as I’m guided to, to help you 

Because the more we talk and share and support each other, the more we heal 

About the hard and the ugly stuff, not just the surface level shit 

I hope you know I’m always always here for you, whether you just read my posts or you’re a long term client or friend 

I love you all soooo much!!!! 🤗🤗💕💕💕

And if you’re a soul led entrepreneur looking for your support system, your confidence, your sisters…

Come join us at the Bougie Beach Retreat April 13-16th! 👯‍♀️🦋🌿

The story of my rebirth, for someone out there who really needs a message of hope today 🦋💜

The last few years the tower has come crumbling down for so many of us

All the old ways of being and doing that are not aligned must go

And if we don’t let go, the Universe will make sure that we do somehow, and that way ain’t usually very pretty (trust me lol)

This has literally been my life the last few years

So much that I spent years to build crumbled and fell away, and I was so mad for so long

I felt lost, alone, confused, and like I would never come out of the cocoon I was in 

I worked hard on my own healing journey and made my embodiment practices a priority 

I prayed, I cried, I yelled at God, and cried some more

Then all of my healing, praying, crying, and embodiment work added up and suddenly my life was brand new 

I became SO FUCKING EXCITED that the old fell away 

Because I know have a chance to focus on what my NEW PASSIONS ARE, I have a more balanced life where I focus on more than just my business, and I manifested the most beautiful tribe and support system that a girl could ever ask for 

If you’ve been navigating these same changes my love, you are not alone, and you WILL get out to the other side

And you are closer than you think 

The feminine frequency is the NEW energy that we are being called to step in to, and this is where all of your desires and manifestations reside 

If you are ready to surround yourself with the support of sisters going through this as well, and ready to heal and rebirth the new version of you…
